OL,3,CFootball managers shine a light on
OL,4,Csuicide prevention
OL,6,FSome of the biggest football managers
OL,7,Facross the country have come together
OL,8,Fto voice their support for a suicide
OL,9,Fprevention campaign.
OL,11,FJurgen Klopp, Pep Guardiola and Eddie
OL,12,FHowe are among a list of footballing
OL,13,Fgreats who have taken part in a new
OL,14,Ffilm to encourage others to know the
OL,15,Fwarning signs and help prevent people
OL,16,Ffrom taking their own lives.
