OL,3,CFootball managers shine a light on
OL,4,Csuicide prevention
OL,6,FIt is part of the Shining a Light on
OL,7,FSuicide campaign run by NHS Greater
OL,8,FManchester and supported by the Mayor
OL,9,Fand the League Managers Association
OL,10,F(LMA).
OL,12,FFeaturing in a new film talking openly
OL,13,Fabout mental health, 50 managers
OL,14,Frepresenting the Women's Super League,
OL,15,FPremier League and English Football
OL,16,FLeague are encouraging people to take
OL,17,Fa free training course.
