OL,3,CFootball managers shine a light on
OL,4,Csuicide prevention
OL,6,FResearch shows that, by asking
OL,7,Fdirectly if a person is thinking of
OL,8,Fsuicide, the risk can be reduced as it
OL,9,Fprovides an opportunity for the person
OL,10,Fto open up about how they are feeling.
OL,12,FAndy Burnham, Mayor of Greater
OL,13,FManchester, said: "Suicide is the
OL,14,Fbiggest killer of young people in this
OL,15,Fcountry, and far too many families are
OL,16,Fliving with the heartbreak it leaves
OL,17,Fbehind.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
