OL,3,CFootball managers shine a light on
OL,4,Csuicide prevention
OL,6,F"We can't accept that - we've got to
OL,7,Fkeep talking about it and make sure
OL,8,Fpeople know help is there when they
OL,9,Fneed it."
OL,11,FThe support for this campaign from
OL,12,Fmanagers started in 2021 and this
OL,13,Fyear, more managers than ever are now
OL,14,Fjoining the campaign.
OL,16,FDr Claire Iveson, Director at the Zero
OL,17,FSuicide Alliance, said: "Suicide
OL,18,Fdoesn't discriminate. It can affect
OL,19,Fanyone, even those who seem to be
OL,20,Fthriving.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
