OL,3,CFootball managers shine a light on
OL,4,Csuicide prevention
OL,6,F"When you're concerned someone might
OL,7,Fbe struggling, it's natural to feel
OL,8,Funsure about what to say or do. But
OL,9,Fnot saying or doing anything can feel
OL,10,Fworse.
OL,12,F"Our suicide awareness training
OL,13,Fcourses have been taken nearly three
OL,14,Fmillion times and aim to help people
OL,15,Fbetter understand suicide risk,
OL,16,Fsuicide warning signs and shares tips
OL,17,Ffor how to approach a conversation
OL,18,Fwith someone they're worried about."
